 ). Recent case studies have estimated ranges of 1.47–2 log
 10 PFU/mL (

  39
 ), 0.49–3.39 log
 10 FFU/mL (

  14
 ), 2.20–2.75 log
 10 PFU/mL, and 1.88–2.80 log
